name: Cetacean Mix
description:
This is a generalist model focused on making wallpapers.

This is my first merge so the quality might not be out there in terms of quality.

If you have any complaints please leave a review so i can improve the model in the next version.

This model can do both SFW and NSFW images.

Things to remember:

  • Please use DPM++ 2M Karras and a good upscaler

  • Does not work well with images depicting motion like parkour, skydiving, fighting, dancing, swimming

  • It prefers to generate static images by default.

  • Please use short prompts, (Longer ones do work but the image has a slight chance to break.)

  • landscape orientation images have a high chance of throwing a signature. I could not get rid of it without breaking the model.

I am not responsible for what you make using this model.
